<p>Researcher Smalls did not attend the latter parts of our testing this evening. He no longer appears on any of our itineraries and his name has been expunged from my project files. If there has been an immediate project alteration or a change in schedule that I was not informed of, please let me know <span style="text-decoration: underline;">immediately</span>.<br /></p>
