<div class="quote-block">
<p>Researcher Calzaroli, are you alright? Yes, there was indeed a 3-hour schedule change, but a &quot;Researcher Smalls&quot; has never been involved with this project. I can assure you &#8212; <span style="text-decoration: underline;">no one</span> named Researcher Smalls has worked with us. Please, John, take a break, the stress must be getting to you. I know that testing has been absolutely <em>cutthroat</em> these past few weeks. I feel it, too.<br /></p>
