<p>But, if you truly claim that there is no Researcher Smalls, well, there must be something more to this. SCP-VERY-META erases anomalies and the files associated with them. We haven't discussed where exactly these anomalies <em>go</em>, and I'm sure we've all had our questions. As far as I can remember, Smalls was assigned to SCP-VERY-META when it was first discovered.</p>
<p>Are we sure personnel aren't also being <span style="color: #f4f4f4;">yeeted</span>?<br /></p>
